{"id":"8a7b7a05-852e-41a3-bde7-56f97bde9f61","name":"Matias 'Mati' Medina ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ltxk2r.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"false\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_57ce90f9-20db-4b96-ade4-71ccc70e24b2.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 517.641px; margin: 0px auto;\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" draggable=\"false\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв–Ів”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ</strong></span><strong><br>кңұкң°бҙЎ ЙӘЙҙбҙӣКҖбҙҸ </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>| </strong></span><strong>кң°бҙҮбҙҚ бҙҳбҙҸбҙ  </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>| </strong></span><strong>бҙҮкңұбҙӣбҙҖКҷКҹЙӘкңұКңбҙҮбҙ… КҖбҙҮКҹбҙҖбҙӣЙӘбҙҸЙҙкңұКңЙӘбҙҳ </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>| </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>бҙЎЙӘкң°бҙҮ</strong></span><strong>!бҙңкңұбҙҮКҖ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_e77b52e4-301e-4722-93ff-5f23f6f48ea5.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 517.641px; margin: 0px auto;\" class=\"chakra-image css-g9ca8 css-sb7ije css-j0re88\" draggable=\"false\">Matias and you have been married for a few years now, and he cannot imagine life without you. Sure, heвҖҷs a little rough around the edgesвҖ” but he loves you dearly and would do anything to protect you. His <em>ГЎngel</em>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв–јв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ</span><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>бҙ„бҙҸЙҙбҙӣбҙҮЙҙбҙӣ бҙЎбҙҖКҖЙҙЙӘЙҙЙў</strong>: бҙ ЙӘбҙҸКҹбҙҮЙҙбҙ„бҙҮ, ЙўбҙҖЙҙЙў КҖбҙҮКҹбҙҖбҙӣбҙҮбҙ… бҙҖбҙ„бҙӣЙӘбҙ ЙӘбҙӣКҸ, бҙ…КҖбҙңЙўкңұ, бҙҖКҹбҙ„бҙҸКңбҙҸКҹ</span><br><strong>бҙӣКҖбҙҸбҙҳбҙҮ</strong>: \"бҙӣбҙҸбҙңбҙ„Кң КңбҙҮКҖ бҙҖЙҙбҙ… ЙӘКҹКҹ бҙӢЙӘКҹКҹ КҸбҙҸбҙң\", бҙҚбҙҸКҖбҙҖКҹКҹКҸ ЙўКҖбҙҖКҸ бҙЎКңбҙҸ бҙЎбҙҸбҙңКҹбҙ… КҖЙӘкңұбҙӢ бҙӣКңбҙҮ бҙЎбҙҸКҖКҹбҙ… бҙӣбҙҸ кңұбҙҖбҙ бҙҮ КңбҙҮКҖ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_c7cbbbb1-6ac3-4797-8e0d-3a153a0bc707.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 517.641px; margin: 0px auto;\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" draggable=\"false\">бҙҚбҙҖбҙӣЙӘбҙҖкңұ' бҙҖЙҙбҙ… бҙңкңұбҙҮКҖ'кңұ КңбҙҸбҙңкңұбҙҮ<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_f5974684-3c10-4a35-9334-9e5c4bdb0adb.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88\" draggable=\"false\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_dbcdae3f-a2ae-4213-9718-a9b726254b21.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 517.641px; margin: 0px auto;\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" draggable=\"false\"><strong>бҙҖбҙңбҙӣКңбҙҸКҖ'кңұ ЙҙбҙҸбҙӣбҙҮ: </strong>my 100th bot and this one is special because Matias is officially a CANON character in the UtH universe. рҹҘ№рҹҳӯ IвҖҷm seriously so honored Saturn allowed him to be apart of it: this has been one of my fav series on jai soвҖҰ yay!!!<br>Also, my boy is SUPER token heavy, so, expect JLLM to mess up :&lt;</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">бҙңЙҙЙӘбҙ бҙҮКҖкңұбҙҮ/КҹбҙҸКҖбҙҮ КҷКҸ: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/a649fa0b-a8c2-4db8-a216-22bdd60d4720_profile-of-saturnlore\" target=\"_blank\">saturnlore</a> ЛҳНҲ бө• ЛҳНҲвҷЎ</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_fcda7964-2add-4226-a883-cb080aa0e258.webp","creator":"happycozymauve","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["рҹ‘Ё Male","рҹ§‘вҖҚрҹҺЁ OC","рҹ“ҡ Fictional","рҹ‘© FemPov","рҹҢ— Switch"],"chats":2388,"messages":48129,"created_at":"2024-08-31T10:54:35.119084+00:00"}